{
    "meta": {
        "editor_label": "$t:sirsoft-gdpr.settings.policy_version.snapshot_modal.editor_label"
    },
    "id": "policy_version_snapshot_modal",
    "comment": "정책 버전 snapshot 모달 — admin 권한자가 v배지/이력 표 행 클릭 시 노출. 부모 layout 의 gdprPolicyVersionSnapshot data_source 가 _global.viewingPolicyVersion 정수를 endpoint path 에 보간하여 그 시점 settings snapshot (cookie_categories / privacy_policy_slug / blocked_domains) 을 표시. DPO 가 회원 분쟁 시 입증 자료로 활용 (GDPR Art.7(1)). Partial 파일에 data_sources 정의 금지 규정 — 부모 layout 에서 정의하고 본 partial 은 컴포넌트만 참조.",
    "type": "composite",
    "name": "Modal",
    "props": {
        "title": "$t:sirsoft-gdpr.settings.policy_version.snapshot_modal.title|version={{_global.viewingPolicyVersion ?? '?'}}",
        "width": "min(720px, 95vw)",
        "closeOnBackdropClick": true
    },
    "children": [
        {
            "type": "basic",
            "name": "Div",
            "props": {
                "className": "row-stack"
            },
            "children": [
                {
                    "comment": "안내문 — DPO 입증 자료 활용 안내",
                    "type": "basic",
                    "name": "P",
                    "props": {
                        "className": "text-secondary text-xs leading-relaxed"
                    },
                    "text": "$t:sirsoft-gdpr.settings.policy_version.snapshot_modal.description"
                },
                {
                    "comment": "메타 — 발행일시 + 발행자 + 변경사유 + 변경 종류 (4개를 grid 2열).",
                    "type": "basic",
                    "name": "Div",
                    "if": "{{gdprPolicyVersionSnapshot?.data?.data}}",
                    "props": {
                        "className": "grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-x-6 gap-y-2 text-xs border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 rounded-md p-3 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-900"
                    },
                    "children": [
                        {
                            "type": "basic",
                            "name": "Div",
                            "props": {
                                "className": "flex items-baseline gap-2"
                            },
                            "children": [
                                {
                                    "type": "basic",
                                    "name": "Span",
                                    "props": {
                                        "className": "text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0"
                                    },
                                    "text": "$t:sirsoft-gdpr.settings.policy_version.published_at_label"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "basic",
                                    "name": "Span",
                                    "props": {
                                        "className": "text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100"
                                    },
                                    "text": "{{gdprPolicyVersionSnapshot?.data?.data?.created_at ?? '-'}}"
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "basic",
                            "name": "Div",
                            "props": {
                                "className": "flex items-baseline gap-2"
                            },
                            "children": [
                                {
                                    "type": "basic",
                                    "name": "Span",
                                    "props": {
                                        "className": "text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0"
                                    },
                                    "text": "$t:sirsoft-gdpr.settings.policy_version.publisher_label"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "basic",
                                    "name": "Span",
                                    "props": {
                                        "className": "text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100"
                                    },
                                    "text": "{{gdprPolicyVersionSnapshot?.data?.data?.publisher?.name ? (gdprPolicyVersionSnapshot?.data?.data?.publisher?.email ? gdprPolicyVersionSnapshot.data.data.publisher.name + ' (' + gdprPolicyVersionSnapshot.data.data.publisher.email + ')' : gdprPolicyVersionSnapshot.data.data.publisher.name) : (gdprPolicyVersionSnapshot?.data?.data?.publisher?.email ?? '$t:sirsoft-gdpr.settings.policy_version.publisher_system')}}"
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "basic",
                            "name": "Div",
                            "props": {
                                "className": "flex items-baseline gap-2"
                            },
                            "children": [
                                {
                                    "type": "basic",
                                    "name": "Span",
                                    "props": {
                                        "className": "text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0"
                                    },
                                    "text": "$t:sirsoft-gdpr.settings.policy_version.history.col.change_type"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "basic",
                                    "name": "Span",
                                    "props": {
                                        "className": "text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100"
                                    },
                                    "text": "{{gdprPolicyVersionSnapshot?.data?.data?.change_type === 'material' ? '$t:sirsoft-gdpr.settings.policy_version.change_type.material' : (gdprPolicyVersionSnapshot?.data?.data?.change_type === 'initial' ? '$t:sirsoft-gdpr.settings.policy_version.change_type.initial' : '$t:sirsoft-gdpr.settings.policy_version.change_type.non_material')}}"
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "basic",
                            "name": "Div",
                            "props": {
                                "className": "flex items-baseline gap-2 min-w-0"
                            },
                            "children": [
                                {
                                    "type": "basic",
                                    "name": "Span",
                                    "props": {
                                        "className": "text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0"
                                    },
                                    "text": "$t:sirsoft-gdpr.settings.policy_version.memo_label"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "basic",
                                    "name": "Span",
                                    "props": {
                                        "className": "text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 truncate"
                                    },
                                    "text": "{{gdprPolicyVersionSnapshot?.data?.data?.memo ?? '-'}}"
                                }
                            ]
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "comment": "정책 본문 슬러그 섹션 — 가장 위로 (정보 위계: 큰 것 → 작은 것). 슬러그가 있으면 평문 + 새 탭 열기 링크 Button, 없으면 안내문.",
                    "type": "basic",
                    "name": "Div",
                    "props": {
                        "className": "row-stack"
                    },
                    "children": [
                        {
                            "type": "basic",
                            "name": "H4",
                            "props": {
                                "className": "text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100"
                            },
                            "text": "$t:sirsoft-gdpr.settings.policy_version.snapshot_modal.section_privacy_policy"
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "basic",
                            "name": "Div",
                            "if": "{{gdprPolicyVersionSnapshot?.data?.data?.snapshot?.privacy_policy_slug}}",
                            "props": {
                                "className": "flex-center gap-2 flex-wrap"
                            },
                            "children": [
                                {
                                    "type": "basic",
                                    "name": "Span",
                                    "props": {
                                        "className": "px-3 py-2 text-xs font-mono text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-900 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 rounded flex-1 min-w-0 break-all"
                                    },
                                    "text": "{{gdprPolicyVersionSnapshot?.data?.data?.snapshot?.privacy_policy_slug ?? '-'}}"
                                },
                                {
                                    "comment": "본문 페이지 새 탭 열기 — 슬러그를 그대로 path 로 사용 (예: 'privacy-policy' → '/privacy-policy'). 운영자가 검증한 슬러그라 사용자 입력 검증 불요.",
                                    "type": "basic",
                                    "name": "A",
                                    "props": {
                                        "href": "/{{gdprPolicyVersionSnapshot?.data?.data?.snapshot?.privacy_policy_slug}}",
                                        "target": "_blank",
                                        "rel": "noopener",
                                        "className": "text-info-soft inline-flex items-center gap-1 px-3 py-2 font-medium bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/30 border border-blue-200 dark:border-blue-700 rounded hover:bg-blue-100 dark:hover:bg-blue-900/50 transition-colors flex-shrink-0"
                                    },
                                    "children": [
                                        {
                                            "type": "basic",
                                            "name": "Span",
                                            "text": "$t:sirsoft-gdpr.settings.policy_version.snapshot_modal.open_policy_page"
                                        }
                                    ]
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "basic",
                            "name": "Div",
                            "if": "{{!gdprPolicyVersionSnapshot?.data?.data?.snapshot?.privacy_policy_slug}}",
                            "props": {
                                "className": "text-tertiary italic px-3 py-2 border border-dashed border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 rounded"
                            },
                            "text": "$t:sirsoft-gdpr.settings.policy_version.snapshot_modal.no_policy_slug"
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "comment": "쿠키 카테고리 섹션 — snapshot.cookie_categories[] iteration. 다국어 객체 (ko/en) / plain 문자열 양쪽 호환.",
                    "type": "basic",
                    "name": "Div",
                    "if": "{{gdprPolicyVersionSnapshot?.data?.data?.snapshot?.cookie_categories}}",
                    "props": {
                        "className": "row-stack"
                    },
                    "children": [
                        {
                            "type": "basic",
                            "name": "H4",
                            "props": {
                                "className": "text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100"
                            },
                            "text": "$t:sirsoft-gdpr.settings.policy_version.snapshot_modal.section_categories"
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "basic",
                            "name": "Div",
                            "if": "{{(gdprPolicyVersionSnapshot?.data?.data?.snapshot?.cookie_categories ?? []).length === 0}}",
                            "props": {
                                "className": "text-tertiary italic px-3 py-2 border border-dashed border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 rounded"
                            },
                            "text": "$t:sirsoft-gdpr.settings.policy_version.snapshot_modal.no_categories"
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "basic",
                            "name": "Div",
                            "if": "{{(gdprPolicyVersionSnapshot?.data?.data?.snapshot?.cookie_categories ?? []).length > 0}}",
                            "props": {
                                "className": "divider-list border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 rounded-md"
                            },
                            "iteration": {
                                "source": "gdprPolicyVersionSnapshot?.data?.data?.snapshot?.cookie_categories ?? []",
                                "item_var": "category"
                            },
                            "children": [
                                {
                                    "type": "basic",
                                    "name": "Div",
                                    "props": {
                                        "className": "px-3 py-2 text-xs space-y-1"
                                    },
                                    "children": [
                                        {
                                            "type": "basic",
                                            "name": "Div",
                                            "props": {
                                                "className": "flex items-baseline gap-2"
                                            },
                                            "children": [
                                                {
                                                    "type": "basic",
                                                    "name": "Span",
                                                    "props": {
                                                        "className": "font-mono text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 font-semibold"
                                                    },
                                                    "text": "{{category?.key ?? '?'}}"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "comment": "라벨 — 다국어 객체 (ko/en) 또는 plain 문자열 양쪽 호환. 객체일 때 ko 우선 추출, 아니면 그대로.",
                                                    "type": "basic",
                                                    "name": "Span",
                                                    "props": {
                                                        "className": "text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400"
                                                    },
                                                    "text": "{{(category?.label && typeof category.label === 'object') ? (category.label.ko ?? category.label.en ?? '-') : (category?.label ?? '-')}}"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "basic",
                                                    "name": "Span",
                                                    "if": "{{category?.required === true}}",
                                                    "props": {
                                                        "className": "ml-auto px-2 py-0.5 text-[10px] font-medium bg-amber-100 dark:bg-amber-900/40 text-warning-soft rounded"
                                                    },
                                                    "text": "$t:sirsoft-gdpr.settings.policy_version.snapshot_modal.category_required_badge"
                                                }
                                            ]
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "comment": "설명 — 다국어 객체 (ko/en) 또는 plain 문자열 양쪽 호환.",
                                            "type": "basic",
                                            "name": "P",
                                            "if": "{{category?.description}}",
                                            "props": {
                                                "className": "text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed"
                                            },
                                            "text": "{{(category?.description && typeof category.description === 'object') ? (category.description.ko ?? category.description.en ?? '') : (category?.description ?? '')}}"
                                        }
                                    ]
                                }
                            ]
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "comment": "차단 도메인 카탈로그 섹션 — 백엔드가 변환한 blocked_domains_list 배열 사용. [{category, domains[]}] 형태. snapshot.blocked_domains 객체를 G7 엔진이 직접 iteration 못하므로 백엔드에서 변환.",
                    "type": "basic",
                    "name": "Div",
                    "props": {
                        "className": "row-stack"
                    },
                    "children": [
                        {
                            "type": "basic",
                            "name": "H4",
                            "props": {
                                "className": "text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100"
                            },
                            "text": "$t:sirsoft-gdpr.settings.policy_version.snapshot_modal.section_blocked_domains"
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "basic",
                            "name": "Div",
                            "if": "{{(gdprPolicyVersionSnapshot?.data?.data?.blocked_domains_list ?? []).length === 0}}",
                            "props": {
                                "className": "text-tertiary italic px-3 py-2 border border-dashed border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 rounded"
                            },
                            "text": "$t:sirsoft-gdpr.settings.policy_version.snapshot_modal.no_blocked_domains"
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "basic",
                            "name": "Div",
                            "if": "{{(gdprPolicyVersionSnapshot?.data?.data?.blocked_domains_list ?? []).length > 0}}",
                            "props": {
                                "className": "divider-list border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 rounded-md"
                            },
                            "iteration": {
                                "source": "gdprPolicyVersionSnapshot?.data?.data?.blocked_domains_list ?? []",
                                "item_var": "blockedGroup"
                            },
                            "children": [
                                {
                                    "type": "basic",
                                    "name": "Div",
                                    "props": {
                                        "className": "px-3 py-2 text-xs space-y-1"
                                    },
                                    "children": [
                                        {
                                            "type": "basic",
                                            "name": "Div",
                                            "props": {
                                                "className": "font-mono text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 font-semibold"
                                            },
                                            "text": "{{blockedGroup?.category ?? '?'}}"
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "type": "basic",
                                            "name": "Ul",
                                            "props": {
                                                "className": "list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 space-y-0.5"
                                            },
                                            "iteration": {
                                                "source": "blockedGroup?.domains ?? []",
                                                "item_var": "domain"
                                            },
                                            "children": [
                                                {
                                                    "type": "basic",
                                                    "name": "Li",
                                                    "props": {
                                                        "className": "font-mono break-all"
                                                    },
                                                    "text": "{{domain}}"
                                                }
                                            ]
                                        }
                                    ]
                                }
                            ]
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "comment": "닫기 버튼 — 일반 dismiss 모달이지만 명시 닫기 버튼 추가 (UX)",
                    "type": "basic",
                    "name": "Div",
                    "props": {
                        "className": "flex justify-end pt-2"
                    },
                    "children": [
                        {
                            "type": "basic",
                            "name": "Button",
                            "props": {
                                "type": "button",
                                "className": "px-4 py-2 text-xs font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 rounded hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 transition-colors"
                            },
                            "actions": [
                                {
                                    "type": "click",
                                    "handler": "closeModal"
                                }
                            ],
                            "children": [
                                {
                                    "type": "basic",
                                    "name": "Span",
                                    "text": "$t:sirsoft-gdpr.settings.policy_version.snapshot_modal.close"
                                }
                            ]
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        }
    ]
}
